<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" itunes:timing="Word"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><iTunesMetadata xmlns="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal"><songwriters><songwriter>TAKU INOUE</songwriter><songwriter>藤原基央</songwriter></songwriters></iTunesMetadata><amll:meta key="musicName" value="ray (超かぐや姫！ Version)"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="かぐや(cv.夏吉ゆうこ)"/><amll:meta key="album" value="超かぐや姫！"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="JPTF02650038"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1869843696"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="3340114786"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="3V5bJpqNCHHi56pGZHNy1f"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="0014t6LS3L9DYp"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="Mrs4s"/></metadata></head><body dur="4:11.071"><div begin="22.429" end="4:11.071"><p begin="22.429" end="25.621" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="22.429" end="22.657">お</span><span begin="22.657" end="23.124">別</span><span begin="23.124" end="23.483">れ</span><span begin="23.483" end="23.791">し</span><span begin="23.791" end="24.257">た</span><span begin="24.257" end="24.482">の</span><span begin="24.482" end="24.718">は</span><span begin="24.718" end="25.141">もっ</span><span begin="25.141" end="25.621">と</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">明明已经分别</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">o wa ka re shi ta no wa mo tto</span></p><p begin="25.621" end="29.021" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="25.621" end="26.286">前</span><span begin="26.286" end="26.491">の</span><span begin="26.491" end="27.184">事</span><span begin="27.184" end="27.646">だっ</span><span begin="27.646" end="27.884">た</span><span begin="27.884" end="28.149">よ</span><span begin="28.149" end="28.327">う</span><span begin="28.327" end="29.021">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">像是早就过去了的往事</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ma e no ko to da tta yo u na</span></p><p begin="29.021" end="32.661" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="29.021" end="29.455">悲</span><span begin="29.455" end="29.930">しい</span><span begin="29.930" end="30.768">光</span><span begin="30.768" end="31.052">は</span><span begin="31.052" end="31.514">封</span><span begin="31.514" end="31.745">じ</span><span begin="31.745" end="31.986">込</span><span begin="31.986" end="32.213">め</span><span begin="32.213" end="32.661">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">将悲伤的光芒封存心底</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ka na shi i hi ka ri wa fu u ji ko me te</span></p><p begin="32.661" end="36.982" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="32.661" end="33.382">踵</span><span begin="33.382" end="33.801">す</span><span begin="33.801" end="34.244">り</span><span begin="34.244" end="34.470">減</span><span begin="34.470" end="34.711">ら</span><span begin="34.711" end="34.941">し</span><span begin="34.941" end="35.394">た</span><span begin="35.394" end="35.615">ん</span><span begin="35.615" end="36.982">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">磨损着鞋跟继续前行</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ka ka to su ri he ra shi ta n da</span></p><p begin="36.982" end="40.146" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="36.982" end="37.430">君</span><span begin="37.430" end="37.647">と</span><span begin="37.647" end="38.112">い</span><span begin="38.112" end="38.338">た</span><span begin="38.338" end="39.048">時</span><span begin="39.048" end="39.258">は</span><span begin="39.258" end="39.484">見</span><span begin="39.484" end="39.712">え</span><span begin="39.712" end="40.146">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">和你在一起时 曾清晰可见</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ki mi to i ta to ki wa mi e ta</span></p><p begin="40.146" end="43.581" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="40.146" end="40.827">今</span><span begin="40.827" end="41.061">は</span><span begin="41.061" end="41.512">見</span><span begin="41.512" end="41.735">え</span><span begin="41.735" end="41.982">な</span><span begin="41.982" end="42.425">く</span><span begin="42.425" end="42.872">なっ</span><span begin="42.872" end="43.581">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如今却已经模糊不清</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">i ma wa mi e na ku na tta</span></p><p begin="43.581" end="47.216" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="43.581" end="44.030">透</span><span begin="44.030" end="44.487">明</span><span begin="44.487" end="44.623">な</span><span begin="44.623" end="45.134">彗</span><span begin="45.134" end="45.637">星</span><span begin="45.637" end="45.817">を</span><span begin="45.817" end="46.016">ぼ</span><span begin="46.016" end="46.282">ん</span><span begin="46.282" end="46.506">や</span><span begin="46.506" end="46.727">り</span><span begin="46.727" end="47.216">と</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那颗透明的彗星 我依稀记得</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">to u me i na su i se i wo bo n ya ri to</span></p><p begin="47.216" end="50.772" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="47.216" end="47.428">で</span><span begin="47.428" end="47.612">も</span><span begin="47.612" end="48.117">そ</span><span begin="48.117" end="48.353">れ</span><span begin="48.353" end="48.790">だ</span><span begin="48.790" end="49.004">け</span><span begin="49.004" end="49.777">探</span><span begin="49.777" end="49.961">し</span><span begin="49.961" end="50.093">て</span><span begin="50.093" end="50.173">い</span><span begin="50.173" end="50.772">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">也唯有它 我至今仍在寻找</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">de mo so re da ke sa ga shi te i ru</span></p><p begin="50.772" end="54.195" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="50.772" end="51.235">しょっ</span><span begin="51.235" end="51.797">ちゅう</span><span begin="51.797" end="52.165">唄</span><span begin="52.165" end="52.645">を</span><span begin="52.645" end="53.576">歌っ</span><span begin="53.576" end="53.813">た</span><span begin="53.813" end="54.195">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我总是不停地唱着歌</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">sho tchu u u ta wo u ta tta yo</span></p><p begin="54.195" end="58.061" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="54.195" end="54.467">そ</span><span begin="54.467" end="54.715">の</span><span begin="54.715" end="55.359">時</span><span begin="55.359" end="55.613">だ</span><span begin="55.613" end="56.080">け</span><span begin="56.080" end="56.326">の</span><span begin="56.326" end="56.547">メ</span><span begin="56.547" end="56.978">ロ</span><span begin="56.978" end="57.428">ディー</span><span begin="57.428" end="58.061">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">唱着只属于那一刻的旋律</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">so no to ki da ke no me ro dii wo</span></p><p begin="58.061" end="1:01.468" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="58.061" end="58.899">寂</span><span begin="58.899" end="59.235">し</span><span begin="59.235" end="59.475">く</span><span begin="59.475" end="59.615">な</span><span begin="59.615" end="59.945">ん</span><span begin="59.945" end="1:00.163">か</span><span begin="1:00.163" end="1:00.370">な</span><span begin="1:00.370" end="1:00.835">かっ</span><span begin="1:00.835" end="1:01.025">た</span><span begin="1:01.025" end="1:01.468">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我从来不觉得寂寞</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">sa bi shi ku na n ka na ka tta yo</span></p><p begin="1:01.468" end="1:05.550" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:01.468" end="1:01.703">ちゃ</span><span begin="1:01.703" end="1:01.978">ん</span><span begin="1:01.978" end="1:02.103">と</span><span begin="1:02.103" end="1:02.998">寂</span><span begin="1:02.998" end="1:03.548">し</span><span begin="1:03.548" end="1:03.758">く</span><span begin="1:03.758" end="1:04.020">な</span><span begin="1:04.020" end="1:04.262">れ</span><span begin="1:04.262" end="1:04.465">た</span><span begin="1:04.465" end="1:04.705">か</span><span begin="1:04.705" end="1:05.550">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">因为我学会了好好感受寂寞</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">cha n to sa bi shi ku na re ta ka ra</span></p><p begin="1:05.550" end="1:09.161" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:05.550" end="1:06.020">い</span><span begin="1:06.020" end="1:06.300">つ</span><span begin="1:06.300" end="1:06.525">ま</span><span begin="1:06.525" end="1:06.761">で</span><span begin="1:06.761" end="1:07.202">ど</span><span begin="1:07.202" end="1:07.431">こ</span><span begin="1:07.431" end="1:07.890">ま</span><span begin="1:07.890" end="1:08.093">で</span><span begin="1:08.093" end="1:08.333">な</span><span begin="1:08.333" end="1:08.573">ん</span><span begin="1:08.573" end="1:09.161">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“要走到何时、何地”</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">i tsu ma de do ko ma de na n te</span></p><p begin="1:09.161" end="1:12.908" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:09.161" end="1:09.910">正</span><span begin="1:09.910" end="1:10.344">常</span><span begin="1:10.344" end="1:10.818">か</span><span begin="1:10.818" end="1:11.018">異</span><span begin="1:11.018" end="1:11.535">常</span><span begin="1:11.535" end="1:11.745">か</span><span begin="1:11.745" end="1:11.973">な</span><span begin="1:11.973" end="1:12.203">ん</span><span begin="1:12.203" end="1:12.908">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“是正常还是异常”</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">se i jo u ka i jo u ka na n te</span></p><p begin="1:12.908" end="1:16.313" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:12.908" end="1:13.540">考</span><span begin="1:13.540" end="1:13.799">え</span><span begin="1:13.799" end="1:14.018">る</span><span begin="1:14.018" end="1:14.718">暇</span><span begin="1:14.718" end="1:15.129">も</span><span begin="1:15.129" end="1:15.360">無</span><span begin="1:15.360" end="1:15.600">い</span><span begin="1:15.600" end="1:16.313">程</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">根本无暇思考</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ka n ga e ru hi ma mo na i ho do</span></p><p begin="1:16.313" end="1:20.165" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:16.313" end="1:16.753">歩</span><span begin="1:16.753" end="1:16.978">く</span><span begin="1:16.978" end="1:17.217">の</span><span begin="1:17.217" end="1:17.444">は</span><span begin="1:17.444" end="1:17.894">大</span><span begin="1:17.894" end="1:18.360">変</span><span begin="1:18.360" end="1:20.165">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">光是走下去就已精疲力竭</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">a ru ku no wa ta i he n da</span></p><p begin="1:20.165" end="1:23.796" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:20.165" end="1:20.732">楽</span><span begin="1:20.732" end="1:21.067">し</span><span begin="1:21.067" end="1:21.296">い</span><span begin="1:21.296" end="1:21.723">方</span><span begin="1:21.723" end="1:21.957">が</span><span begin="1:21.957" end="1:22.448">ずっ</span><span begin="1:22.448" end="1:22.656">と</span><span begin="1:22.656" end="1:22.843">い</span><span begin="1:22.843" end="1:23.128">い</span><span begin="1:23.128" end="1:23.796">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">快乐一点总比什么都好</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ta no shi i ho u ga zu tto i i yo</span></p><p begin="1:23.796" end="1:27.418" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:23.796" end="1:24.256">ご</span><span begin="1:24.256" end="1:24.486">ま</span><span begin="1:24.486" end="1:24.660">か</span><span begin="1:24.660" end="1:24.962">し</span><span begin="1:24.962" end="1:25.368">て</span><span begin="1:25.368" end="1:26.053">笑っ</span><span begin="1:26.053" end="1:26.281">て</span><span begin="1:26.281" end="1:26.753">いく</span><span begin="1:26.753" end="1:27.418">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就算勉强 也会笑着走下去</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">go ma ka shi te wa ra tte i ku yo</span></p><p begin="1:27.418" end="1:30.863" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:27.418" end="1:27.884">大</span><span begin="1:27.884" end="1:28.335">丈</span><span begin="1:28.335" end="1:28.579">夫</span><span begin="1:28.57